ARE HAPPY ENOUGH.

01:06.316 --> 01:07.568
OH, NONSENSE.

01:07.651 --> 01:09.062
THEY'RE ONLY
COVERING UP.

01:09.152 --> 01:11.018
THEY'RE SAD,
UNHAPPY CHILDREN.

01:11.113 --> 01:13.525
THEY HAVE NO BASE,
THEY HAVE NO ANCHOR.

01:13.615 --> 01:15.151
THEY HAVE
NO DIRECTION.

01:15.242 --> 01:17.404
THEY'RE LIKE LITTLE
FLOTSAM AND JETSAM.

01:17.452 --> 01:18.988
NEDRA, IT TAKES TIME.

01:19.079 --> 01:21.070
ANNE NEEDS MORE TIME.

01:21.164 --> 01:22.325
SO DO I.

01:22.416 --> 01:23.497
YOU'VE <i>HAD</i> TIME.

01:23.584 --> 01:25.040
THIS IS RIDICULOUS.

01:25.127 --> 01:26.993
ANNE'S PROBLEM IS
A KIND OF SICKNESS,

01:27.087 --> 01:28.919
