<i>WE'VE BEEN EXPECTING YOU.</i>

06:08.034 --> 06:09.365
[loud whirring]

06:10.704 --> 06:13.446
[Click]

06:13.540 --> 06:16.032
JUST TO CONVINCE YOU
THAT FACSIMILE LIMITED

06:16.126 --> 06:19.460
