IT CLAIMS THAT IT CAN.

06:19.546 --> 06:22.959
THIS WAY, PLEASE.

06:23.049 --> 06:24.505
[clicks]

06:24.593 --> 06:29.633
EYES-- SOFT BROWN,
VIVID BLUE.

06:29.723 --> 06:34.308
ANY COLOR YOU CHOOSE.

06:34.394 --> 06:35.725
[click and whirr]

06:35.812 --> 06:39.476
HAIR-- WHITE, GREY,
RED, BROWN.

06:39.566 --> 06:41.182
AREN'T THEY BEAUTIFUL?

06:44.988 --> 06:46.399
[click and whir]

06:46.448 --> 06:50.362
EARS-- ALL SIZES,
ALL SHAPES.

07:05.926 --> 07:08.258
SLENDER OR STURDY.

07:13.266 --> 07:14.643
SHORT OR TALL.

07:24.277 --> 07:26.143
THIS CAN'T BE...

07:26.237 --> 07:28.103
OH, NO.

07:28.198 --> 07:30.109
THESE ARE JUST
THE BITS AND PIECES.

07:30.158 --> 07:32.616
JUST THE EYES,
THE LIPS, THE LIMBS

07:32.661 --> 07:34.618
FROM VVHIOH YOU VVILL
CHOOSE THE ELEMENTS

07:34.663 --> 07:36.370
WHICH WILL
BECOME YOUR, UH...

07:36.456 --> 07:38.367
GRANDMOTHER?

07:38.458 --> 07:40.199
<i>YOU MEAN WE GET TO
PICK OUT THE COLOR</i>

07:40.293 --> 07:41.875
OF EYES
SHE'LL HAVE?

07:41.962 --> 07:43.293
AND HOW TALL?

07:43.380 --> 07:44.791
