07:44.839 --> 07:46.250
YOU WILL
PICK THEM OUT...

07:48.301 --> 07:51.293
AND PUT THEM
DOWN THIS CHUTE

07:51.388 --> 07:53.345
VVHERE THEY VVILL BE
CONVEYED TO OUR FACTORY.

07:53.431 --> 07:55.968
