IS TOO HIGH.

08:27.507 --> 08:31.421
<i>(deep bass female voice) "I
CELEBRATE MYSELF AND SING MYSELF."</i>

08:31.511 --> 08:33.092
AGAIN, WALT WHITMAN.

08:33.179 --> 08:36.261
TOO LOW.

08:36.349 --> 08:40.183
<i>(medium female voice) "THE ARMIES
OF THOSE I LOVE ENGIRTH ME,</i>

08:40.270 --> 08:42.010
<i>AND I ENGIRTH THEM."</i>

08:42.063 --> 08:43.394
THAT'S JUST RIGHT.

08:43.481 --> 08:48.396
THAT'S IT.

08:48.486 --> 08:50.602
COULD YOU BUILD HER
LIKE MY MOTHER?

08:50.697 --> 08:51.687
IF YOU WISH.

08:51.781 --> 08:53.192
EXACTLY LIKE HER?

08:53.241 --> 08:54.857
YES.

08:54.951 --> 08:55.736
<i>(Anne) THEN I DON'T WANT HER.</i>

08:55.827 --> 08:57.693
ANNE.

08:57.746 --> 09:00.534
I DON'T VVANT HER TO BE LIKE MY MOTHER.
I'D HATE HER.

09:00.582 --> 09:01.913
<i>ANNE, PLEASE.</i>

09:02.000 --> 09:03.240
EXCUSE ME.

09:03.334 --> 09:05.917
[whirring]

09:06.004 --> 09:09.122
TOM, YOU VVANT HER TO LOOK
LIKE MOTHER, DON'T YOU?

09:09.215 --> 09:10.671
SURE.

09:10.759 --> 09:12.215
