WHAT ANNE THINKS.

09:12.260 --> 09:16.720
NAH, SHE'S CRAZY.

09:16.806 --> 09:19.218
I CAN WIN ANY GAME
OF MARBLES WITH THOSE,

09:19.309 --> 09:24.429
