HAD LONG HAIR.

09:43.083 --> 09:44.494
[whirring]

09:47.962 --> 09:49.418
[whirring]

10:22.705 --> 10:24.537
HEY, AGGIES.

10:24.624 --> 10:26.865
BROWN AGGIES.

10:26.960 --> 10:30.453
I CAN WIN ANY GAME
OF MARBLES WITH THOSE.

10:30.505 --> 10:33.372
YOU MUST BE
TOM AND KAREN,

10:33.466 --> 10:36.208
<i>AND THAT'S ANNE,
