OLD MACHINE!

15:38.938 --> 15:42.272
ANNE. ANNE, YOU'D
BE SURPRISED, MY DEAR,

15:42.316 --> 15:43.772
HOW MUCH
A MACHINE CAN DO

15:43.860 --> 15:45.976
