15:51.993 --> 15:53.279
YOU, ANNE.

15:53.369 --> 15:55.451
I CAN LOVE YOU,
AND I DO.

15:55.496 --> 15:58.204
I LOVE YOU MORE THAN...

15:58.291 --> 16:00.828
MORE THAN
TONGUE CAN TELL.

16:00.918 --> 16:02.454
<i>YOU DON'T LOVE ME.</i>

16:02.545 --> 16:03.706
<i>YOU CAN'T.</i>

16:03.796 --> 16:05.878
SHE SAID
SHE LOVED ME.

16:05.965 --> 16:07.296
SHE?

16:07.341 --> 16:08.797
MY MOTHER.

16:08.885 --> 16:10.626
SHE SAID,
"I LOVE YOU,"

16:10.720 --> 16:12.051
BUT SHE LIED.

16:12.138 --> 16:13.720
SHE LIED!

16:13.806 --> 16:15.547
AND YOU'RE
LIKE HER.

16:15.641 --> 16:18.224
